<body>
<div type="chapter" n="67">
<div>
<p>副使治<placeName>甘州</placeName>
<pc>，</pc>領都知河西兵馬使<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>置興平<term>節度使</term>
<pc>，</pc>領<placeName>上洛</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>安康<pc>、</pc>武當<pc>、</pc>房陵<num value="4">四</num>郡<pc>，</pc>治<placeName>上洛</placeName>郡<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>升<placeName>夔州</placeName>防禦為夔峽<term>節度使</term>
<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>以夔<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>峽</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>忠<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>歸</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>
<measure quantity="5" unit="prefectures">
<num value="5">萬五</num>州</measure>隸<placeName>夔州</placeName>
<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>荊南節度復領澧<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>朗</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>忠</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>峽<measure quantity="4" unit="prefectures">
<num value="4">四</num>州</measure>
<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>罷<placeName>武</placeName>關內外<measure quantity="4" unit="prefectures">
<num value="4">四</num>州</measure>防禦<term>觀察使</term>
<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>置夔忠涪都<term>防禦使</term>
<pc>，</pc>治<placeName>夔州</placeName>
<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>置劍南西山<term>防<placeName>禦</placeName>使</term>
<pc>，</pc>治茂<placeName>州</placeName>
<pc>，</pc>未幾廢<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>復以<measure quantity="15" unit="prefectures">
<num value="15">十五</num>州</measure>還東川節度<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>廢定邊軍<term>節度使</term>
<pc>，</pc>復以巂<pc>、</pc>眉<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>蜀</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>邛</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>雅</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>嘉</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>黎</placeName>
<measure quantity="7" unit="prefectures">
<num value="7">七</num>州</measure>隸西川節度<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>置<placeName>彭州</placeName>
<term>防禦使</term>
<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>置武定軍<term>節度使</term>
<pc>，</pc>治<placeName>洋州</placeName>
<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>置興文<term>節度使</term>
<pc>，</pc>領興<pc>、</pc>文<pc>、</pc>集<pc>、</pc>壁<measure quantity="4" unit="prefectures">
<num value="4">四</num>州</measure>
<pc>，</pc>治興州<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
</div>
</body>
